{"word":"G4485 - ῥῆγμα - rhēgma - hrayg'-mah - Ruin","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ῥῆγμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>rhēgma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hrayg'-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Ruin"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அழிவு - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. a fracture, breach, cleft"},{"paragraph":"2. torn clothes"},{"paragraph":"3. fall, ruin"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4486 - ῥήγνυμι - rhḗgnymi - hrayg'-noo-mee/4486\">G4486</a>; something <i>torn</i>, that is, a <i>fragment</i> (by implication and abstraction, a <i>fall</i>): - ruin."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}